snippet.title: 7 Actresses Who Could Replace Amber Heard as Mera in Aquaman 2
snippet.description:
In this video, we are going to talk about 7 actresses who can replace Amber Heard as Mera in Aquaman 2. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
____________________________________________

It looks like the Hollywood career of Amber Heard will be over soon. Amber Heard has reportedly been fired from Aquaman 2 because of her continuing legal dispute with her ex-husband Johnny Depp. According to the sources, Heard was also removed from other future Warner Brothers projects. 

It’s not unusual for roles to get recast for huge franchises like this, but a lot could be accomplished with someone else stepping in as the Queen of Atlantis.

___________________________________________
